propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesAlignLeft: Styles applied to the root element if `align="left"`.
stylesAlignRight: Styles applied to the root element if `align="right"`.
stylesAlignAlternate: Styles applied to the root element if `align="alternate"`.
stylesMissingOppositeContent: Styles applied to the root element if no there isn't TimelineOppositeContent provided.
stylesContent: Styles applied to the timeline content node.
stylesOppositeContent: Styles applied to the timeline opposite content node.
